'''[[東盎格利亞|東盎格利亞]]的氣候'''總體上是乾燥和溫和的。該地區是英國最乾燥的地區之一，許多地區年降雨量不足700毫米<ref name="metoffee">[http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/ee/print.html Eastern England: climate] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/ee/print.html |date=20110605044423 }}, Met Office. Retrieved 2014-02-15.</ref>，[[洛斯托夫特|洛斯托夫特]]等地平均降雨量甚至不足600毫米<ref name="low71">[http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/sites/lowestoft.html Lowestoft 1971–2000 averages] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/sites/lowestoft.html |date=20111019064917 }}, Met Office. Retrieved 2014-02-15.</ref>。全年降雨量分佈相當均勻。

最高温度在冬季為5-10°C（41-50°F），夏季為20-25°C（68-77°F），不过据了解最高温度可达到35°C（95°F）。沿海地区的日照总量往往较高。<ref>Brown, Chris [http://www.cambridgeshire.gov.uk/environment/policy/Env_Report_1998.htm State of the Environment Report 1998] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506231548/http://www.cambridgeshire.gov.uk/environment/policy/Env_Report_1998.htm|date=2008-05-06}} Chapter 11: Physical Background (pp. 305–306) Cambridgeshire County Council (retrieved 19 July 2007)</ref>
